    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219180/extras/210c56e8dcbc9f08f0a553f87ae9ffd7.avif?t=1771535770\" width=800 height=424 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219180/extras/a4b240b1ee9b0498c3bc83b42a14ad56.poster.avif?t=1771535770\" width=834 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219180/extras/a4b240b1ee9b0498c3bc83b42a14ad56.webm?t=1771535770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219180/extras/0fffe7fda9a6a319764c10141fa19b3d.avif?t=1771535770\" width=616 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗紧凑而冷冽，对敌交互诚实可感，闪避与硬直彼此度量。你需以步伐丈量距离，以时机切开命运；读懂敌人的节拍，打断其高举的仪式，或让其在你的刃上完成告别。<br><i>每一场胜负都由你亲手缝合，每一次失手都在你身上刻下可见的教训</i>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219180/extras/874845e97d4a3bd10e01a859416987c3.poster.avif?t=1771535770\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219180/extras/874845e97d4a3bd10e01a859416987c3.webm?t=1771535770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219180/extras/874845e97d4a3bd10e01a859416987c3.mp4?t=1771535770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219180/extras/365bf54937e5ae9ceb593b1e52399b90.avif?t=1771535770\" width=616 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >火山深渊，古老官邸，仍滴落着熔岩；白雪荒原，冰封王城，沉眠在风暴之中；泥泞的沼泽，半沉的古建筑，喃喃不息；沙漠尽头，孤山如墓碑般刺向苍穹；黑暗森林，阴森大宅，静候陌生的脚步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>每一步偏行，皆是对真相的逼近。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219180/extras/4dbdf9108bab6459dac9758fcde30d7c.poster.avif?t=1771535770\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219180/extras/4dbdf9108bab6459dac9758fcde30d7c.webm?t=1771535770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219180/extras/4dbdf9108bab6459dac9758fcde30d7c.mp4?t=1771535770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219180/extras/37105f07da09291dc4cde7fe71f77ea7.avif?t=1771535770\" width=616 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >法术与符文如骨与血般相缚。多种法术与符文相互搭配，同一束火焰可化为散落的星雨，也可汇成贯穿长夜的炽枪。请在游戏中尽情探索每一个法术无限的可能性，用绚丽多彩的咒术洪流摧毁胆敢拦在你身前的敌人</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>魔法的伟大在于无穷无尽的想象力</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219180/extras/9161084919a2393275d26e8c5ee89ced.poster.avif?t=1771535770\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219180/extras/9161084919a2393275d26e8c5ee89ced.webm?t=1771535770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219180/extras/9161084919a2393275d26e8c5ee89ced.mp4?t=1771535770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219180/extras/46044e2d20d51a8f331767e9b1e7050c.avif?t=1771535770\" width=616 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里的死亡并非终点，而是回响。每次倒下让你归于赐福之前，都在你体内累积不可逆的经验与构筑，新的符印被唤醒，新的路线被开启，新的法术跃然纸上，新的誓约在篝火边悄然系上。当你再次迈步，旅途已不再与初见相同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>杀不死我的，终将使我更加强大。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219180/extras/931d2fa753fbdfb979c592764f00e66c.poster.avif?t=1771535770\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219180/extras/931d2fa753fbdfb979c592764f00e66c.webm?t=1771535770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219180/extras/931d2fa753fbdfb979c592764f00e66c.mp4?t=1771535770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>命运的轮盘，既无终点，亦无解脱；命运的馈赠，比王的铁链更沉重。</i><br></p>",
